1. **Analyze and Describe the Main Target Image:**

   The main image shows two structures.  Focusing on the structure on the left, it is composed of four blocks. There are two layers.  The bottom layer comprises an orange arched block (likely #2 or #3 from the dictionary) and a slanted orange triangle block (likely #13).  On top of that layer is a green rectangular block (#7)  and another slanted orange triangle block (#13).
